Package: barqueReport
Title: Tools for Metabarcoding Report Generation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Steve", "Vissault", "", "steve.vissault@inrs.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for processing and reporting metabarcoding data 
    from the barque bioinformatics pipeline. This package streamlines the analysis 
    workflow by providing functions to load and process species identifications table, fetch 
    taxonomic and conservation information from multiple databases (NatureServe, 
    ITIS, GBIF, Catalogue of Life), generate summary statistics, and create 
    interactive visualizations.
